reviewText: great shows for kids
Fast delivery, good product. My grandchildren love the WILD KRATTS

This DVD contains only 2 episodes from the Wild Kratts cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Termites vs. Tongues - Exploring termites and their predators.
2. Bugs or Monkeys - The Kratts must save a baby spider monkey.
